PN,41901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779274977
OL,3,CLevels of 'forever chemicals' in the
OL,4,CSolent are 13 times higher than EU
OL,5,Climits
OL,7,FEnvironmental campaigners have warned
OL,8,Fthat so-called ' forever chemicals'
OL,9,Fare present in levels that exceed
OL,10,Fcurrent safety limits in parts of the
OL,11,FSolent.
OL,13,FAlso known as PFAS, they are used in
OL,14,Feveryday products such as non stick
OL,15,Fcookware and waterproof coats and do
OL,16,Fnot easily break down in the
OL,17,Fenvironment - so they end up in our
OL,18,Fwaterways.
OL,20,FThe latest warning follows testing by
OL,21,Fthe University of Portsmouth.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779274977
OL,3,CLevels of 'forever chemicals' in the
OL,4,CSolent are 13 times higher than EU
OL,5,Climits
OL,7,FResearch by the university and the
OL,8,FMarine Conservation Society tested for
OL,9,Fpolyfluoroalkyl substances (PFAS) in
OL,10,Fthe Solent - a stretch of water
OL,11,Fbetween Portsmouth and the Isle of
OL,12,FWight.
OL,14,FIt found PFAS were present in the
OL,15,Fwater, sediment and throughout the
OL,16,Ffood cycle.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779274977
OL,3,CLevels of 'forever chemicals' in the
OL,4,CSolent are 13 times higher than EU
OL,5,Climits
OL,7,FLevels of one of the most tightly
OL,8,Fregulated compounds - PFOS - exceeded
OL,9,Fthe UK and European Union (EU) legal
OL,10,Fsafety limit for coastal waters by
OL,11,Fmore than 13 times at the sampling
OL,12,Fsites tested.
OL,14,FProfessor Alex Ford from the
OL,15,FUniversity of Portsmouth's Institute
OL,16,Fof Marine Sciences, said: "We are
OL,17,Fseeing chemicals throughout the
OL,18,FSolent's food web, from the base right
OL,19,Fup to marine mammals.
OL,26,@xD@[OU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779274977
OL,3,CLevels of 'forever chemicals' in the
OL,4,CSolent are 13 times higher than EU
OL,5,Climits
OL,7,F"Current treatment processes are not
OL,8,Fdesigned to remove these substances
OL,9,Feffectively."
OL,11,FThe study also mapped around 194
OL,12,Fcombined sewer overflow (CSO) outfall
OL,13,Fpoints and 546 historic landfill sites
OL,14,Fin close proximity to the Solent,
OL,15,Fhighlighting the scale of potential
OL,16,Fsources feeding PFAS into the coastal
OL,17,Fsystem.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779274977
OL,3,CLevels of 'forever chemicals' in the
OL,4,CSolent are 13 times higher than EU
OL,5,Climits
OL,7,FAmong the marine wildlife tested,
OL,8,Fharbour porpoises showed the highest
OL,9,FPFAS concentrations, with levels in
OL,10,Fliver tissue far exceeding the
OL,11,Fregulatory ecological threshold.
OL,13,FLevels in fish, invertebrates,
OL,14,Fseaweeds, and other species were lower
OL,15,Fand, when judged against individual
OL,16,Fcompound limits, mostly within legal
OL,17,Fboundaries.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779274977
OL,3,CLevels of 'forever chemicals' in the
OL,4,CSolent are 13 times higher than EU
OL,5,Climits
OL,7,FBut researchers said that when they
OL,8,Fapplied a more comprehensive approach
OL,9,F- adding up the combined effect of all
OL,10,Fforever chemicals detected and
OL,11,Fexpressing them as a single toxicity
OL,12,Fmeasure - the picture "changed
OL,13,Fsignificantly".
OL,15,FProfessor Ford added: ''We are seeing
OL,16,Fforever chemicals throughout the
OL,17,FSolent's food web, from the base right
OL,18,Fup to marine mammals.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779274977
OL,3,CLevels of 'forever chemicals' in the
OL,4,CSolent are 13 times higher than EU
OL,5,Climits
OL,7,F''Most species fall within the legal
OL,8,Flimits when you look at individual
OL,9,Fchemicals in isolation, but when you
OL,10,Fconsider everything together, the
OL,11,Fpicture is more concerning.''
OL,13,FA Defra spokesperson said: "The
OL,14,Fpersistent nature of 'forever
OL,15,Fchemicals' poses a long-term challenge
OL,16,Ffor the nation's ecosystems and health.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
