FL,420,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1779274977
OL,3,CLevels of 'forever chemicals' in the
OL,4,CSolent are 13 times higher than EU
OL,5,Climits
OL,7,F"The first ever PFAS Plan shows the
OL,8,Fdecisive action we are taking to
OL,9,Fbetter understand and tackle the
OL,10,Fsources of these chemicals, including
OL,11,Fin England's estuaries and coastal
OL,12,Fwaters, through better guidance and
OL,13,Fmonitoring, tougher rules on their use
OL,14,Fand support for transitioning to safer
OL,15,Falternatives."
